Fun and relaxation lounge, Dynasty Lounge, recently celebrated it esteemed customers by feeding over one thousand of them free of charge. The Lounge which hosted well acclaimed Nigerian celebrities, including; Zlatan Ibile, Teni, Tunde Ednut and others recently, is located around Delta Mall, Warri, Delta state. According to the founder, High chief Arthur Eyitemi Diden, it was necessary to celebrate his trusted customers, and appreciate them for their patronage. He said it was also a way to celebrate the valentine season of love with them. He said; ‘I just wanted to use the opportunity to celebrate and appreciate my customers for their continued patronage and support, which has helped in building this lounge. Also, this is Valentine season, a time to show love, so in other words I am telling my customers that I love them.”